Package Project3

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Company
    The Company class is used to store all of the current employees in array format.
    Controller
    The Controller class is used to control the Payroll Processor GUI and implement all the methods of Company.
    Date
    The Date class is used to represent dates in the format mm/dd/yyyy.
    Employee
    This class represents an employee at a company.
    Fulltime
    This class represents a full-time employee at a company.
    Main
    The Main class is used to set the stage and run the Payroll Processor GUI.
    Management
    This class represents a management employee at a company.
    Parttime
    This class represents a part-time employee at a company.
    Profile
    This class represents an employee profile.
